      <title>德国工业生产的下降胜于二月份的预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/german-industrial-production-fell-more-than-expected-in-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的工业生产在2月份的下降超出了预期，强调了该国主要部门已经在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的积极贸易政策的新逆风之前所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/german-industrial-production-fell-more-than-expected-in-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 06:12:35 GMT</pubDate>
