    <item>
      <title>自上次贸易战争以来，中国停止了美国液化天然气进口最长的进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-halts-us-lng-imports-in-longest-run-since-last-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已经60天从美国进口了液化天然气，这是五年来最长的差距，因为北京和华盛顿之间的关系恶化，使美国的买家转移了货物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-halts-us-lng-imports-in-longest-run-since-last-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 04:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税战争升级时，中国股票“恐慌卖”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股票和公司债券暴跌，而主权收益率却接近了历史最低水平，因为投资者为世界上两个最大经济体之间螺旋式贸易冲突做出了贡献。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾的股票在假期返回时遭受创纪录的抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/tsmc-slumps-10-on-tariff-woes-as-taiwan-returns-from-holiday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的股票指数最多，有记录在记录的熊市，因为假期后恢复了交易，并抓住了唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税远足触发的全球抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/tsmc-slumps-10-on-tariff-woes-as-taiwan-returns-from-holiday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金亿万富翁在鲁特加深时抨击特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/ackman-calls-trump-tariffs-a-mistake-and-massively-in-excess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼（Bill Ackman）和斯坦利·德鲁肯（Stanley Druckenmiller）抨击唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统决定发起广泛的全球关税，这使市场陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/ackman-calls-trump-tariffs-a-mistake-and-massively-in-excess</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 23:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票溃败恶化，债券在关税动荡上集会：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股票的飞行加速了，投资者堆积在避风港资产中，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税加深了中国宣布报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国呼吁平静，新鲜计划应对特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/china-floats-rate-cuts-industry-aid-to-counter-trump-tariff-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税加息，中国警告不要恐慌，称其有足够的政策室来捍卫经济，但不排除与美国进行谈判。]]></description>
